msgstr "R-kuadrat"

msgid "Conceptual path plot"
msgstr "Diagram jalur konseptual"

msgid "Statistical path plot"
msgstr "Diagram jalur statistikal"

msgid "Model syntax"
msgstr "Sintaksis model"

msgid "Model must be a directed acyclic graph -- it must not contain loops."
msgstr ""
"Model harus berada di grafik akrilik langsung -- itu tidak harus berisi "
"pengulangan."

msgid "%1$s: Hayes configuration %2$s not implemented"
msgstr "%1$s: Konfigurasi Hayes %2$s tidak diimplementasikan"

msgid "Estimation failed because of an internal error."
msgstr "Estimasi gagal karena galat internal."

msgid "Full Information Maximum Likelihood estimation only available with 'ML' or 'Auto' estimators. Please choose a different estimator or option for missing value handling."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi Kemungkinan Maksimum Informasi Lengkap hanya tersedia dengan "
"estimator 'ML' atau 'Otomatis'. Silakan pilih estimator berbeda atau opsi "
"untuk penanganan nilai hilang."

msgid "<li>Some implied model variances are > 1,000,000</li>"
msgstr "<li>Beberapa varians model bersirat adalah > 1,000,000</li>"

msgid "<li>Some implied model variances are at least a factor 1000 times larger than others</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li>Beberapa varians model bersirat adalah setidaknya faktor 1000 kali lebih "
"besar dari lain</li>"

msgid "The information matrix could not be inverted. This may be a symptom that the model is not identified. Possible reasons: <ul>%s</ul>"
msgstr ""
"Matriks informasi tidak dapat dibalikkan. Ini mungkin berupa simptom bahwa "
"model tidak diidentifikasikan. Alasan memungkinkan: <ul>%s</ul>"

msgid "At least one model is incomplete or no model is specified. Please add at least one model and complete specified models."
msgstr ""
"Setidaknya satu model tidak lengkap atau tidak ada model ditentukan. Silakan "
"tambahkan setidaknya satu model dan selesaikan model tertentu."

msgid "The AIC, BIC and additional information criteria are only available with ML-type estimators."
msgstr ""
"AIC, BIC dan kriteria informasi tambahan hanya tersedia dengan estimator "
"jenis-ML."

msgid "<b>Important</b>: Parameter estimates can only be interpreted as causal effects if all confounding effects are accounted for and if the causal effect directions are correctly specified."
msgstr ""
"<b>Penting</b>: Estimasi parameter hanya dapat diinterpretasikan sebagai "
"efek kausal jika semua efek perancu dihitung dan jika arahan efek kausal "
"secara benar ditentukan."

msgid "Please check the model specification and lavaan syntax."
msgstr "Silakan periksa spesifikasi model dan sintaksis lavaan."

msgid "Linear test type cannot be applied to factor variables. Choose a different test type or remove all factor variables from the model."
msgstr ""
"Jenis pengujian linear tidak dapat diterapkan ke variabel faktor. Pilih "
"jenis pengujian berbeda atau hapus semua variabel faktor dari model."

msgid "The specified model does not imply any (conditional) independencies that can be tested."
msgstr ""
"Model tertentu tidak menyiratkan independen (kondisonal) apa pun yang dapat "
"diuji."

msgid "Partially standardized estimate because effect involves categorical predictor."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi terstandardisasi secara parsial karena efek melibatkan prediktor "
"kategorikal."

msgid "Moderation effect estimates are based on mean-centered variables."
msgstr "Estimasi efek moderasi berdasarkan variabel terpusat-rerata."

msgid "Confidence intervals are %s bootstrapped. Standard errors, <em>z</em>-values and <em>p</em>-values are based on the delta method."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan %s terbootstrap. Galat standar, nilai-<em>z</em> dan "
"nilai-<em>p</em> berdasarkan metode delta."

msgid "Not all bootstrap samples were successful: CI based on %.0f samples."
msgstr "Tidak semua sampel bootstrap berhasil: CI berdasarkan %.0f sampel."

msgid "Model does not contain moderated indirect effects for<br>which the moderated medation index can be calculated."
msgstr ""
"Model tidak berisi efek tidak langsung termoderasi yang<br>mana indeks "
"meditasi termoderasi dapat dihitung."

msgid "<em>p</em>-values adjusted for multiple comparisons with the %s method."
msgstr ""
"nilai-<em>p</em> disesuaikan untuk beberapa perbandingan dengan metode %s."
